{"tid":1738901,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【傾唔成】據報特朗普不願取消關稅　中國對達成貿易協議感悲觀","createTime":"2019-11-19T11:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T17:04:00.000Z","uid":14328,"like":329,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ca5fcb79e138aeabcaa89dc77bc0b1f6b5ccb9","tid":1738901,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493185-20191119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493185-20191119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=bb2bbc28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493185-20191119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=92f15ec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493185-20191119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國財經頻道CNBC引述消息指，由於美國總統特朗普未肯如中方所願，取消向中國貨加徵的關稅，中方亦拒絕承諾購買特定數量的農產品。目前中方正密切注視美國的政治局勢，包括國會對特朗普展開的彈劾調查、明年總統大選的結果。外界對貿易戰可以迅速完結，愈來愈不感樂觀，預計今年內全球經濟增長仍然會保持疲弱。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網站Twitter表示，與聯儲局主席鮑威爾在白宮展開非常友好的會議，討論議題包括中美貿易、國內的負利率、低通脹、量寬政策等。對於特朗普過去一直批評鮑威爾的利率政策，聯儲局發表聲明重申，將根據法律要求制定貨幣政策，以維持最高的就業率與價格穩定。<br />\n<br />\n華為對美國商務部將禁令推遲90日執行的決定，表示對實際經濟影響有限。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1493185_1_L_20191119115552.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1493185_1_L_20191119115552.jpg&h=5b9cf8ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c06b90fb00ce6704335bb9d5feb4ea577671f280","tid":1738901,"uid":146030,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"一定傾唔到<br />\n敵我鬥爭嚟"},{"pid":"2e9fbeeb87537506fc8e366893da38951069e01d","tid":1738901,"uid":198783,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"朗普點會肯取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=