包括國會對特朗普展開的彈劾調查、明年總統大選的結果。外界對貿易戰可以迅速完結，愈來愈不感樂觀，預計今年內全球經濟增長仍然會保持疲弱。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網站Twitter表示，與聯儲局主席鮑威爾在白宮展開非常友好的會議，討論議題包括中美貿易、國內的負利率、低通脹、量寬政策等。對於特朗普過去一直批評鮑威爾的利率政策，聯儲局發表聲明重申，將根據法律要求制定貨幣政策，以維持最高的就業率與價格穩定。<br />\n<br />\n華為對美國商務部將禁令推遲90日執行的決定，表示對實際經濟影響有限。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1493185_1_L_20191119115552.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1493185_1_L_20191119115552.jpg&h=5b9cf8ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買豬肉都冇錢落訂，傾佢老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>[/b]"},{"pid":"6c71732f4d8c8cc1c020802f022561b132ba7df0","tid":1738901,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0650bceae22352dd6d04f84c81675568de74523e","tid":1738901,"uid":261505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7F3KHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7F3KHM.jpg&h=05d6fbd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1728bf02533efc0c991acbdeda81b0db033b8a9","tid":1738901,"uid":297453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"不平等條約 傾唔傾得成 支那都係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e5357505d66a8fd34deff08028774a4c49822a","tid":1738901,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db169ea54b5005ea14cc37aeec0fb71f816b1